name: My Favorite Place To Be
description:
Sun rises through trees
reveling the seas,
the seasons have started to change.
Light moving through them 
and on them and over,
shapes from dark shadows turn strange.
Green, orange, gold -
red, purple, blue.
These spectrums of color,
can you feel them, too?
The seasons like me
float effortlessly.
This is my favorite place to be.
